title: Brookelyn Farthing
description:
18 year-old Brookelyn Farthing was last seen at a home in Berea, Kentucky in the early morning hours of June 22, 2013.  Shortly before she disappeared, she sent several texts indicating that she was scared.  That morning, the home that she was last seen at suspiciously caught fire.  If you have any information about Brooke's disappearance, please call the Kentucky State Police at 859-623-2404 or 1-800-222-5555.  You can also send tips through Missing: Brookelyn Farthing on Facebook or findbrookeky@gmail.com.

See Privacy Policy at https://art19.com/privacy and California Privacy Notice at https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info.
